type: dataset
title: "Validated H₇ (Evolutionary Progression) Component for Historical K(t) Coherence Index"
abstract: >
  This dataset provides a validated empirical operationalization of the H₇
  (Evolutionary Progression) component of the historical K(t) coherence index,
  integrating four dimensions of societal advancement: education, innovation
  (patents), infrastructure, and governance. The dataset covers 159 countries
  from 1996-2021 (2,352 observations) and demonstrates that direct empirical
  measurement yields more conservative assessments than demographic proxies,
  strengthening scientific credibility through methodological rigor. Includes
  complete data pipeline (191,913 raw data points from World Bank), processing
  scripts, and K(t) framework integration demonstrating -7.0% conservative
  difference from synthetic approaches.

